Nagios(Monitoring Tool)
About Nagios
	Agent based monitoring
	Monitor Infrastructure
		Servers
		system resources CPU MEMORY SWAP
		devices
		network switches


System requirements
-Supports only Centos or Redhat(6 or 7 versions)
-OS need to be a minimal installation
(http://centos.mirror.net.in/centos/7.5.1804/isos/x86_64/CentOS-7-x86_64-Minimal-1804.iso)
-2GB RAM
-40GB HDD

Two Versions
	Nagios core
	Nagios XI

